metadata.developer: Palm One Group & The Simpson Organization
property_details: Introducing The Gallery Sarasota, a new pinnacle of city living, where sophistication meets convenience in the heart of downtown Sarasota. With 60 exquisite residences, you’ll find an unparalleled living experience that blends modern elegance with seamless access to this coastal destination’s vibrant offerings. Elegance and comfort intertwine effortlessly at The Gallery Sarasota, where six thoughtfully curated floor plan collections set a new standard in design. This limited and purposeful design approach not only enhances the uniqueness of each residence but also contributes to The Gallery’s long-term value and strong resale potential. Seamlessly integrated into downtown Sarasota, The Gallery Sarasota offers unmatched proximity to the waterfront, the Bay Conservancy, and the thriving culinary, shopping, and entertainment scene that define the area. Whether you seek cultural enrichment, gastronomic delights, or strolls by the water, everything is here.
amenity_details: At The Gallery Sarasota, residents are treated to a bevy of top-tier amenities. The tranquil oasis of the private rooftop terrace pool and social lounge provides an elevated retreat for socializing, unwinding, and basking in sun drenched splendor while the vast two-room state-of-the-art fitness center and yoga studio provides an all-encompassing environment for a healthy lifestyle.
developer_details: Under construction and developed by Palm One Group & The Simpson Organization, The Gallery Sarasota is led by a dynamic team of professionals, each bringing their unique expertise and vision to the project. This collective of developers, architects, designers, and sales share a unified commitment to excellence, ensuring that every facet of The Gallery is meticulously crafted. As they join forces, the outcome is certain: The Gallery Sarasota will stand as a true masterpiece, a testament to the power of collaboration and visionary design.
architect_details:
HALFLANTS + PICHETTE   is an award-winning modern design-build studio with offices in Sarasota and Tampa. Our goal is to create thoughtful, high-quality modern architecture that responds to context and function. Our collaborative approach to modern architecture is process-oriented and deliberately avoids preconceived solutions. Halflants + Pichette provides a range of services that include architectural design, interior design,  master planning,  and full construction services. We treasure the diversity of our firm. We hail from nine countries across four continents, and speak five different languages. 

The firm’s work is centered primarily on housing projects and single-family residences, many of which are carried out as design-build ventures. Since its inception, the firm was honored with over fifty American Institute of Architects awards, more than any other practice in the State of Florida. The practice has also garnered five national medals from the Association of Licensed Architects as well as the Tampa Bay AIA Firm of the Year award. Halflants+ Pichette Studio for Modern Architecture has been recognized in the professional press at both state and national levels. The work was published in nine issues of the Florida Caribbean Architect, the quarterly regional publication of the AIA.

On four separate occasions, a residence completed by Halflants + Pichette was featured as the publication’s cover. The work has also been illustrated in Dwell Magazine, AIArchitect, and Residential Architect. In 2017, the AIA honored John Pichette with the Annual Builder of the Year award for the State of Florida. The following year, Michael Halflants was recognized with the AIA Florida Medal of Honor for Design, the highest award for a design that AIA Florida can bestow on an architect.
builder_details: Established in 1987, Voeller Construction is a full-service South Florida-based general contractor focused on a results-centric philosophy.  We have a passion for elevating the business of building to ensure an exceptional experience for all our clients. With over three decades of experience and a solid reputation for reliability and excellence, our SIX88 Sarasota team is dedicated to exceeding expectations through an unrivaled commitment to ensuring that each client’s individual vision is brought to life with precision and care.
